Get Rhythm Privacy Policy

Get Rhythm was developed by Coe Code LLC as a free app. This app is provided through Apple's App Store and is intended for use as is.

Data storage

Linc does not collect nor share any data from its users. All data provided to Linc is stored locally using Apple's CoreData container. In order to keep data in sync between your devices, this app uses Apple's CloudKit container.
